title: [East Row, Ebonwood Way]
description: Passing beyond a tall brick brewery to the northwest, a row of scraggly new ebonwood trees line the pathway heading east, while a broad fel tree marks the road to the north.

Passing beyond a tall brick brewery to the northwest, a heavy shadow casts the area in a neutral light.  A row of scraggly new ebonwood trees line the pathway heading east, while a broad fel tree marks the road to the north.
